{"tid":1402541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］登打士街貢茶唔歡迎黑衫人買野飲","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:55:49.000Z","uid":296789,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8fddf40a8b20e3086a3aca19e731f62c24895d","tid":1402541,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"時間大約係8點半<br />\n由佐敦行到去旺角已經好口渴<br />\n又見到路人拎住杯珍珠奶茶<br />\n小妹忍唔住都想買杯<br />\n飲食係基本人類需要黎咖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就貪近去左貢茶<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位呀叔一開始已經西口西面<br />\n我以為佢係忙所以先咁樣<br />\n但我一直企喺度等落單佢都冇理我<br />\n我都係諗住佢係忙所以未得閒<br />\n直至我身後有個外藉女士排隊<br />\n條仆街就叫佢上前問佢要咩<br />\n但果位女士落完order之後<br />\n又再繼續擰轉身扭毛巾呀沖野飲呀<br />\n完全唔理我<br />\n我諗我都等左大約5分鐘 跟住忍唔住喺佢門口大嗌：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢間鋪頭唔做生意呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之後我同fd行開買第二間<br />\n條友仲一路睥住我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通我用珍奶衝擊佢間鋪咩 點解要咁對我喎"},{"pid":"046f8785e8c287fc7ee825a1f99cbf70c241d9bb","tid":1402541,"uid":152242,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"貢茶好撚難飲 罷飲唔到😂"},{"pid":"0cf6e160b958755621c31c268a2df3d7c7f1ce03","tid":1402541,"uid":143151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呀叔仲要做貢茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f9266b294b06e64f4a85d255d1b384f9695eee","tid":1402541,"uid":296789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"046f8785e8c287fc7ee825a1f99cbf70c241d9bb","tid":1402541,"uid":152242,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"貢茶好撚難飲 罷飲唔到😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:35:35.000Z","msg":"貪近 同埋廿蚊大大杯嘛 其他好貴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb834f57730487fb2071